Package net.sf.marineapi.nmea.sentence

Provides interfaces for NMEA 0183 sentences.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
BODSentence Interface for BOD sentence type.
DateSentence Common interface for sentences that contain UTC date information.
GGASentence Interface for GGA sentence type.
GLLSentence Interface for GLL sentence type.
GSASentence Interface for GSA sentence type.
GSVSentence Interface for GSV sentence type.
PositionSentence Common interface for sentences that contain geographic location (lat/lon).
RMBSentence Interface for RMB sentence type.
RMCSentence Interface for RMC sentence type.
RTESentence Interface for RTE sentence type.
Sentence Base interface and constants for NMEA 0183 sentences.
TimeSentence Interface for sentences that provide current UTC time.
WPLSentence Interface for WPL sentence type.
VTGSentence Interface for VTG sentence type.
ZDASentence Interface for ZDA sentence type.
 

Class Summary
NMEA Utility methods for general sentence operations.
 

Enum Summary
SentenceId Defines the supported NMEA 0831 sentence types.
TalkerId Talker defines the supported NMEA Talker IDs.
 

Package net.sf.marineapi.nmea.sentence Description
